<Big> Map brought to you by Crackshot </big>

This is my first map ever done with Hammer, I am very please with how this map turned out, the map is not based off any real location, but it is based on Realism so if you are interested in playing realistic maps that are all about fighting the other team without an objective, then this map is for you! Please make sure to leave feedback if you play this map! im very interested in getting any tips or ideas for future maps and im gonna count on you folks to help me with that! so please leave your thoughts!
